---
title: Baked Beef & Corn Quesadillas with Salsa & Sour Cream
description: These easy beef quesadillas cook all at once in the oven — perfect for a family dinner. Add the bold Tex-Mex flavours you know and love, plus a bright and zesty corn salsa and rich sour cream and these will quickly be your new favourites.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-baked-beef-quesadillas-eef250f3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/oven-baked-beef-quesadillas-5de8319e52742743d554e13f-c861c8a7.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/baked-beef-and-corn-quesadillas-5de8319e52742743d554e13f
